{"tid":1725513,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如聽日一齊圍剿二橋既恐怖分子","createTime":"2019-11-15T18:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T19:07:12.000Z","uid":16719,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6753076336ced31f359aa7cc3d667d18a8dc1a","tid":1725513,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:31:43.000Z","msg":"呢班校外假前線根本唔是手足<br />\n分分鐘係政府安排既奸細滲透中大<br />\n佢地破壞中大既校園設施 擅自駕駛巴士<br />\n恐嚇火燒學生會人 大學宿舍<br />\n最離譜既是襲擊市民 根本是恐怖分子、叛軍之所為<br />\n但普羅大眾會以為呢班失控既人係中大學生<br />\n再咁搞落去市民會對學生失去信任<br />\n亦會使到政府重建威信  使黑警用更強硬手段清場<br />\n<br />\n所以希望聽日一齊圍剿恐怖分子<br />\n俾香港市民知道 真示威者同學生都討厭呢班人所作所為"},{"pid":"bca0b224a71d1672e7a2fb27da24d60ea8719aa5","tid":1725513,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:33:33.000Z","msg":"一齊清除路障，方便市民出入。"},{"pid":"f92f491b384412837fb0e76a9e2bcbbafc7f00c4","tid":1725513,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"保護圖書館藏書"},{"pid":"792945fef28fbe7b2daeddd2dc9809ecf0231b3f","tid":1725513,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:34:31.000Z","msg":"保護學校樹木"},{"pid":"419a668fefcababaae9201c6a50892da27a2448f","tid":1725513,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:34:56.000Z","msg":"驅逐共諜"},{"pid":"b9f5893d8438d5abad72a82759dd470a6dfab125","tid":1725513,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:35:57.000Z","msg":"圍剿完班內鬼之後，就返屋企。流水鬥爭，不守城池"},{"pid":"5abe04686e6d1de9fffc7ea04c21d302624a8347","tid":1725513,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"做多左"},{"pid":"2a2f24d35a9ff1ac4b1896512ec4b69416acdc86","tid":1725513,"uid":186811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T18:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e3099a47ddb299ada42b3acd220c23ff046e8c","tid":1725513,"uid":16